  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text ">
    UK benefits if you're going or living abroad
  </h1>
</div>

  </header>
  <div class="article-container group">
    
    <div class="content-block">
      <div class="inner">
        
  <section class="intro">
    <div class="get-started-intro">
<p>Find out which UK benefits you might be able to get while you’re abroad and how to claim them.</p>

<p>The UK has social security agreements with some countries that:</p>

<ul>
  <li>allow you to claim UK contribution-based benefits while you’re there</li>
  <li>mean that your National Insurance contributions can count towards your eligibility for that country’s benefits</li>
</ul>

<p>It’s easier to organise benefits before you leave.</p>

<div role="note" aria-label="Information" class="application-notice info-notice">
<p>You must meet the benefit’s eligibility criteria to get it.</p>
</div>
</div>
